            {
               "text": "<p><span id=\"htZoomImageMsg\"></span></p><p><h3>Prerequisites</h3>In this text, we explore the concept of equality. For more details, we recommend starting with:</p><p><ul><li><htcite0>: show how we change from our fingers to geometric pictures.</li><li><htcite1>: Here are the numbers we use today.</li><li><htcite2>: Illustrating the relationship between our ancestors and numbers.</li><li><htcite3>: In this text, we examine the direction in which Indigenous peoples write their numbers.</li><li><htcite4>: This section introduces the reader to the names of generations and numerical orders.</li></ul></p>",
