            },
            {
               "text": "<p>Mesoamerican pyramidal structures, rich in detail, were often used as ceremonial centers and were known to the inhabitants as \"sacred mountains\" (<i>Witz</i>) (<htcite0>).</p>",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "960e3a8e-3a60-4ee4-9df4-e2187489e3b9",
                     "text": "García Capistrán, H.",
